-- Best Buy posts higher profit
-- 
-- Tue Dec 18, 2007 8:09am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/12/18/us-bestbuy-results-idUSWNAS481020071218

 

 ATLANTA  (Reuters) - Consumer electronics retailer Best Buy Co ( BBY.N ) posted a higher-than-expected third-quarter profit on Tuesday on strong sales and raised its full-year earnings forecast. 

 Third-quarter earnings came to $228 million, or 53 cents a share, compared with $150 million, or 31 cents a share, a year earlier. (Reporting by  Karen Jacobs ; editing by John Wallace)